}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The '''[[Broadcom]]''' logo, "BCM94319WLUSBN4L", "U98Z058", and "000101" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
It's may be solely synonymous with [[HP SDGOB-0991 (1150-7933)]], but it has it's own FCC ID. The [[HP SDGOB-0991 (1150-7933)]] is silkscreened with its' own FCC ID: B94SDGOB0991.
